  "text": "Other branches of work related to temporal action localization attempt to solve different variations of the problem, such as detecting temporal extents without explicit temporal annotations [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] , or simultaneously detecting temporal and spatial boundaries [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] .",
